de.intarsys.security.smartcard.card

Class ATR

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.intarsys.security.smartcard.card.ATR

  • public class ATR
extends java.lang.Object
    A wrapper for the "Answer to reset" byte stream. The ATR is signaled with the "CardInserted" event from the PCSC layer.
